            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>Ad&#603;n nti na w&#596;nka no aman mu s&#603;:</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>&#400;he na w&#596;n Nyankop&#596;n no w&#596;?</content>
            </block_quote>
            <content> </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="18">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Na afei AWURADE twee n’asase ho ninkunu,</content>
